Approach I (the entirety of residual spectra) - EIOT_exclusive_signature_PB_star3.m
Approach II (only the best residual spectra)- EIOT_exclusive_signature_PB_star2.m
Approach III (an optimal set of residual spectra) - EIOT_exclusive_signature_PB_star1.m

Example codes for project F - approach III
for i=1:29
ind=ones(311,1);
ind(1:129)=0;
ind(159:end)=0;
ind(130+i-1)=0;
ind=logical(ind);
temp=SPEC_COMBINE.data(CLASS_COMBINE(:,2)==130+i-1,:);
for j=1:10
OUTPUT=EIOT_exclusive_signature_PB_star1(snv(K_Fene),RES_COMBINE_mean(ind,:),snv(temp(j,:)),Sim_Fene_snv);
Temp2.r_hat(j,:)=OUTPUT.r_hat(:,1:size(K_Fene,1));
Temp2.PACLS_pred(j,:)=OUTPUT.PACLS_pred(:,1:size(K_Fene,1));
Temp2.EIOT_ssr(j,:)=OUTPUT.EIOT_ssr;
Temp2.EIOT_ssr_relative(j,1)=OUTPUT.EIOT_ssr_relative;
Temp2.NAS_T(j,1)=OUTPUT.NAS_T;
Temp2.PACLS_ssr(j,:)=OUTPUT.PACLS_ssr;
Temp2.PACLS_ssr_relative(j,1)=OUTPUT.PACLS_ssr_relative;
Temp2.lamda_eqlin(j,1)=OUTPUT.lamda.eqlin;
Temp2.lamda_lower(j,:)=OUTPUT.lamda.lower(1:size(K_Fene,1))';
Temp2.lamda_upper(j,:)=OUTPUT.lamda.upper(1:size(K_Fene,1))';
Temp2.EIOT_res(j,:)=OUTPUT.EIOT_res;
Temp2.PACLS_res(j,:)=OUTPUT.PACLS_res;
Temp2.SND(j,1)=OUTPUT.SND;
end
RESULTS.EIOT_pred(i*10-9:i*10,:)= Temp2.r_hat;
RESULTS.PACLS_pred(i*10-9:i*10,:)= Temp2.PACLS_pred;
RESULTS.EIOT_ssr(i*10-9:i*10,:)= Temp2.EIOT_ssr;
RESULTS.EIOT_ssr_relative(i*10-9:i*10,1)= Temp2.EIOT_ssr_relative;
RESULTS.NAS_T(i*10-9:i*10,1)= Temp2.NAS_T;
RESULTS.PACLS_ssr(i*10-9:i*10,:)= Temp2.PACLS_ssr;
RESULTS.PACLS_ssr_relative(i*10-9:i*10,1)= Temp2.PACLS_ssr_relative;
RESULTS.lamda_eqlin(i*10-9:i*10,:)=Temp2.lamda_eqlin;
RESULTS.lamda_upper(i*10-9:i*10,:)=Temp2.lamda_upper;
RESULTS.lamda_lower(i*10-9:i*10,:)=Temp2.lamda_lower;
RESULTS.EIOT_res(i*10-9:i*10,:)=Temp2.EIOT_res;
RESULTS.PACLS_res(i*10-9:i*10,:)=Temp2.PACLS_res;
RESULTS.SND(i*10-9:i*10,1)=Temp2.SND;
i
end


